Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.20,0:00:06.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This video is a special release provided to all of you by Shounen Sunday!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.49,0:00:12.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you watch this video, brighten the room and don't sit too close to the screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.93,0:00:25.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}One day in the spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.55,0:00:28.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran and I accepted an invitation from Hattori and Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.89,0:00:30.81,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}to visit Osaka yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:38.65,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This time we were supposed to be there purely for sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:44.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}So, first, we went to the Floating Garden Observatory that overlooks all of Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:47.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.78,0:00:49.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the famous Six Gods Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.99,0:00:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And over there, the thing that looks small from here, is the Akashi-Kaikyo Bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.67,0:00:57.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that, can you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.25,0:01:00.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the Osaka International Airport.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next up is Expoland...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:05.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's Osaka Dome...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.93,0:01:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tsuuten Tower...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.43,0:01:10.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Osaka Castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.56,0:01:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.35,0:01:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A great place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.23,0:01:15.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Osaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.81,0:01:23.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Jeez, these two are so alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.73,0:01:31.49,Title,,0,0,0,,CONAN, HEIJI, AND THE VANISHED BOY
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.12,0:01:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right, to the next spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.70,0:01:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Over here, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:45.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.84,0:01:47.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were there when we came by earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.47,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? Those three...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.81,0:01:57.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They look just like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.02,0:02:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're that high school detective Hattori Heiji, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.86,0:02:10.22,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My name is Esaka Mayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:11.43,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Esaka Mayumi (7)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm in my first year of elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:15.72,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The skinny kid is Yagi Mikihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.64,0:02:16.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yagi Mikihiko (7)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.04,0:02:19.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The fat one is Osawa Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Osawa Kenta (7)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.29,0:02:23.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi, Mitsuhiko, Genta?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayumi, Mikihiko, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:29.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got something wrong with your ears!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:33.97,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even their names are eerily similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should see a doctor if there's something wrong with your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of doctors, I went to mine yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:43.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"This cavity isn't good..."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.02,0:02:45.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Looks like we'll have to yank it."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:48.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:49.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.90,0:02:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But my grandpa is even cooler!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.41,0:02:54.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He pulls his teeth out every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.91,0:02:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are dentures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.00,0:02:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You two are so noisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:03:00.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kenta's story was so lame!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.34,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Looks like their personalities are different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.92,0:03:08.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're looking for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:10.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And want my help?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.47,0:03:14.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the gist of it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To be specific, we're looking for a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're hoping you can find out where Satoshi is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.40,0:03:24.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's our friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.65,0:03:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We agreed to meet at the bench\Nout there at 1:00, but he didn't show.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:30.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,1:00, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already past 2:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Did you call his parents?}Have you contacted his family, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.20,0:03:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We tried but got the answering machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy probably stood us up and is still playing around at his secret place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secret place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:49.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he'd be there until noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.38,0:03:54.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's at where the train from the red line\Npasses in front of the T-Rex's hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:58.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though it's really fun, that place sometimes can make you cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.18,0:04:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how Satoshi said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's probably a "CONT".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:05.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's "HINT".
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:10.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In Osaka, the only line with red trains is the Kanjo Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.24,0:04:12.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.24,0:04:15.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the Kanjo Line, you can transfer to the Yumesaki Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's it! I know it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's US...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,USJ is wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:27.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,USJ - Universal Studio Japan, the Japanese amusement park of Universal Studios
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:26.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that was it at first, too,\Nbut he said it was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:31.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What could it be, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not familiar with Osaka's railways...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.85,0:04:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you see a T-Rex model or a billboard of one from the Kanjou Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just, I remember hearing that people in Osaka love those types of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.61,0:04:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed, there are giant crabs, octopi, pufferfish and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.36,0:04:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, no dinosaurs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.74,0:04:59.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Heiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one way to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go take a ride on the Kanjo Line now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Today, we've got two guests...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine with us.{we don't mind at all!}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.96,0:05:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.59,0:05:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to what Heiji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-niichan{\r} has shown us so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this may actually be interesting.{This will be much more interesting.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.14,0:05:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.64,0:05:22.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You bastard... I'll remember this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.11,0:05:35.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hairpin is really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:36.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can I see it for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:38.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi gave it to me.{DCTP: Satoshi gave me this.}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.95,0:05:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A present from your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:01.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is so embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.35,0:06:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:11.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the Floating Garden Observatory that we were just at.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.44,0:06:12.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.98,0:06:14.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,T-Rex, T-Rex...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, did I just see a highway going through that building?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Interesting, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.58,0:06:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Osaka basically has it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:31.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If that's so, even a dinosaur wouldn't look out of place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:34.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the mountains!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.55,0:06:37.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's so special about mountains?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.55,0:06:41.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it, it's because people from Tokyo hardly get to see the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.85,0:06:51.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see any T-Rex billboards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.49,0:06:59.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:04.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kudo, did you see the white car stopped in front of the police cars just then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.04,0:07:07.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it was a Sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The bank robbers' car!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:20.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This morning at 11:30,\Na credit union in Namba was robbed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.76,0:07:23.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminals were a young couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their car was a white Sedan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.77,0:07:30.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's have them handle the dinosaur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our stop's coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Our" stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, what're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.40,0:07:43.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We saw you from the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:45.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the bank robber's car, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, an eyewitness remembered part of the license plate number.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, the criminals switched cars here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:57.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy, aren't you that one...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.80,0:08:00.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.05,0:08:01.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, you're always like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:09.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}'s daughter, I believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:10.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.89,0:08:13.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.36,0:08:21.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:23.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A red hairpin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.41,0:08:27.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That hairpin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.03,0:08:28.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as Mayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.95,0:08:30.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This little girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.83,0:08:33.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.00,0:08:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.79,0:08:38.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're very similar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:43.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little girl, where did you buy this hairpin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.63,0:08:45.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't buy it, someone gave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:48.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone gave it to you? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.56,0:08:49.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.85,0:08:52.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he found it at his secret place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.48,0:08:54.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Secret place?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.90,0:09:01.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.57,0:09:03.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you all took the Kanjo Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.57,0:09:07.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hairpin found in the car must've been dropped by the criminals, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.62,0:09:09.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That seems likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.24,0:09:13.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Both of them were wearing ski masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It probably flew in the car when the woman was taking her mask off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.21,0:09:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, given this little girl's pin\Nand the one the woman dropepd...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.80,0:09:24.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think we can reach a conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By looking at the hairpins, you can tell they were both painted red later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.81,0:09:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The female criminal probably painted them with nail polish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:40.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you use your fingernails\Nto scratch at it, it should peel off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.53,0:09:45.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.57,0:09:50.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The secret place where Satoshi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May somehow be connected to the criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.54,0:10:00.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, does Satoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} make a habit of breaking plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.13,0:10:01.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, this is the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Satoshi didn't show,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:11.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's likely he ran into the criminals at his secret place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, this could be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.52,0:10:18.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminals have guns...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.81,0:10:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knows what they're capable of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But still, we can't be sure of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.07,0:10:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, let's go to the kid's house and check.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With this, we can completely kiss out working days goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:49.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but what're we gonna do with this brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:51.87,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Moriguchi Satoshi (7)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.14,0:10:55.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's seen our faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.18,0:10:56.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't leave a witness behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.18,0:11:01.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to take him up\Ninto the mountains and finish him off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.75,0:11:01.71,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Maejima Tsuyoshi (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.05,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,How pitiful, but I guess we have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.42,0:11:08.38,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Komiya Kaoru (21)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,Moriguchi
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.09,0:11:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an impressive house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was only built recently, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.76,0:11:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As we thought, no one's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.68,0:11:39.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If only his mom were home...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.68,0:11:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We might be able to figure out where Satoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s secret place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.07,0:11:51.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The flowers have dried up...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.32,0:11:52.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.37,0:11:56.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's only one lock on the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.79,0:11:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.87,0:12:02.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could relax knowing that there's a security system in place, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.58,0:12:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you kids know where Satoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s father works?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:07.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.84,0:12:14.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. Oh well, with some investigating, it'd be easy to figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.30,0:12:17.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} doesn't go to the same school we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi goes to a private school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We go to a public one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.48,0:12:24.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how do you all know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We met him at a nearby pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.73,0:12:31.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When we first met him,\NSatoshi was looking up at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.46,0:12:51.26,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hey, look up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:58.93,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Those clouds look like a rabbit and a turtle chasing each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.43,0:13:00.18,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.72,0:13:02.52,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.53,0:13:15.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What an unusual kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:25.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r}, we'll get back on the Kanjo Line to look for the T-Rex.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:41.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji, how'd it go on your end?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:43.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not well, couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.56,0:13:47.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Same here. We split up but still couldn't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We even went as far as the Yomiuri TV building.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.23,0:13:52.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't see anything like a T-Rex.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.23,0:13:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it wasn't the Kanjo Line after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.60,0:13:57.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trains here are more like orange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did Inspector Otaki come up with anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.91,0:14:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During his call just then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he said they were able to find Satoshi's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:12.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, it seems he has no idea where the secret place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did he say Satoshi's father did for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he's a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.26,0:14:23.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He started his own business few years ago, and recently moved into that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:27.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Satoshi isn't very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:36.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recently he complained that his father works too much and fights with his mother all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi looked like he was gonna cry.{He was almost crying when saying that.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.24,0:14:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I just remembered something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:48.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the museum in Nagai,\NI saw a large dinosaur skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:49.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of Nagai...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.42,0:14:55.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's south of Tennoji...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is where the Midosuji Line\Nand the Hagane Subway Line intersect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:01.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the Midosuji Line cars have a red stripe on them!{And the trains to Midosuji have a red stripe on their bodies.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.93,0:15:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.56,0:15:07.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The line's color on the guide map is red!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.98,0:15:11.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, by "red train", he meant the Midosuji Line?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:15.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, Nagai isn't far from Satoshi's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.40,0:15:16.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This has gotta be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a dinosaur, but...{This is, of course, a dinosaur, but...}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.00,0:15:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a T-Rex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.42,0:15:36.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Found it! It's the T-Rex!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is useless, this one has no hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, this was wrong as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:54.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Heiji, it's getting dark out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red train wasn't pointing\Nto the Midosuji Line either, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:06.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the T-Rex!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:12.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at the layout of the route lines, don't they look like a standing T-Rex?{Look at the line diagram. They look a lot like a standing T-Rex, don't they?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.00,0:16:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really does!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:18.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's the body...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And here are the hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can really see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the station "in front of the hands" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.89,0:16:32.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nakamozu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.36,0:16:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what does Nakamozu have over the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.57,0:16:44.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Otaki{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-han{\r} said he would go ask the boy's father,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I hope we'll know before we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:47.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:49.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's only one lock on the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.13,0:16:58.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just expected them to have a double-lock...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.96,0:17:01.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because Satoshi always carries two keys around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:08.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One of them is normal key, but the other has long teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:12.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.60,0:17:13.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.39,0:17:15.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That might be the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:21.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got it, Hei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.53,0:17:22.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Moriguchi family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.94,0:17:24.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Used to live in Nakamozu, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.20,0:17:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right, but how'd you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, it was what we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}They lived in an apartment near Shinnou Pond...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:41.21,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's called{DCTP: it was called} Nankaisho.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.78,0:18:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mind handing over the kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:11.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who're you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.63,0:18:24.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:09.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.01,0:19:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.85,0:19:14.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}! Mikihiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Kenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.39,0:19:16.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything will be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:21.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You all saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.40,0:19:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were so worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This appartment was apparently only occupied by these two criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.62,0:19:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since Satoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has the key to the room from when he used to live here,{Since Satoshi-kun still had the key to the old house even after moving out,}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:48.11,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,He sometimes comes back here by himself.{he sometimes came here by himself.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.88,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Moriguchi Yosuke (38)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.90,0:19:49.88,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Moriguchi Yoshiko (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.88,0:19:52.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would Satoshi do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.95,0:19:54.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it'd be best...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.43,0:19:58.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you two, his parents, found out for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.82,0:20:10.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the middle of this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a dining table.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.49,0:20:16.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad was over there, Mom was over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.33,0:20:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I sat right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:28.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom, you look even more beautiful today!{today you look more beautiful than ever!}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.92,0:20:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've always been beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.84,0:20:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kenta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} can be that pet, Noraya, who used to come over a lot to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.19,0:20:45.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Noraya was a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.33,0:21:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said that in this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.41,0:21:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Even though it's really fun, it's also a place that can make you cry."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.11,0:21:32.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satoshi, we've come to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.53,0:21:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom and Dad! Don't you have work to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:39.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, no more work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.11,0:21:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go get Satoshi's favorite food before we go home, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.08,0:21:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd be great!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.63,0:23:22.09,Signs,,0,0,0,,Neyagawa City - Days Later
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.59,0:23:22.09,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's what happened, it felt great.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.10,0:23:24.94,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Bizen Heishiro (34)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.60,0:23:24.93,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You did a good thing here, Hei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.85,0:23:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I originally planned to bring those two here for some takoyaki before they returned to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.40,0:23:33.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forgot again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:35.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bringing them here next time'll make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.15,0:23:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give them special service.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.30,0:23:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many thanks, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.53,0:23:45.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You brought us souvenirs?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.20,0:23:46.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm touched, Conan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:47.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is is eel on rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.33,0:23:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.37,0:23:51.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is for Mayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:52.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is for you, Kenta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.25,0:23:54.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And this one's yours, Mikihiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.09,0:23:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.30,0:23:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kenta?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.21,0:23:57.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mikihiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:03.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, did something weird happen to you in Osaka?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.77,0:24:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe it did...
